latestIgtvVideos.title: One white Saree 5 Indian States
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey guys!! So in this video I hv styled my old solid boring saree uniquely with respect to different Indian States.I always like the idea of how in each state, people wear different types of clothes, speaks different languages, celebrates different festivals, have different culture, yet India is one united state.
If we talk about clothing then one can see variety of clothing styles in India. Clothing style varies from state to state.
So in this video I have tried to show a bit about different states styling.Hope you will like it ☺️
Please like and share if you like my effort 💞
